biffex member to ballot on merger member of the baltic intern freight futur exchang ( biffex ) are to be ballot at the end of thi week on whether it will merg with the london commod exchang or come under a new umbrella of baltic futur exchang , a biffex offici said . the final decis will be left with the biffex board , which will meet at the end of thi month , he said . last week three exchang current trade on the baltic exchang , the london potato futur associ , the gafta soya bean meal futur associ and the london meat futur exchang , instruct legal advis to implement a merger .